"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_suffering_specter_Description"	"Spectre deeply remembers the suffering she endured, temporarily storing a portion of the damage dealt by <font color='#e80000'>Counter Spell</font>. She can actively cast it on an enemy to clear all stored damage and release a spectral shadow that damages the target and nearby enemies, dealing %base_damage% + stored damage. Passively provides bonus health.<br><br>When cast at night, the casting range becomes global. Damage dealt to distant enemy heroes cannot exceed %penalty_damage_max_pct%%% of the target's maximum health.<br><br>Unaffected by spell amplification."
